                                     <span>Intermarché - Wanty - Gobert Matériaux</span>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <time>00:01:14</time>\n                                </div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <div>\n                                    <div>\n                                        <span>5</span>\n                                        <div>\n                                            <a href=\"#\">TILLER Rasmus</a>\n                                            <span>Uno-X Pro Cycling Team</span>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <time>00:01:14</time>\n                                </div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <a href=\"/race-result?race=256719\">Full results →</a>\n                </div>\n\t\t\t\t            </div>\n\t\t    </div>\n\t\n\n\n\n<figure><ul><li><figure><img src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/antwerp-port-epic-2021-1-1340x894.jpg\" /><figcaption>Van der Poel was the star attraction at the Belgian one-day race.</figcaption></figure></li><li><figure><img src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/antwerp-port-epic-2021-3-1340x894.jpg\" /><figcaption>“Hmm, how will I win this one?”</figcaption></figure></li><li><figure><img src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/antwerp-port-epic-2021-4-1340x870.jpg\" /></figure></li><li><figure><img src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/antwerp-port-epic-2021-5-1340x894.jpg\" /></figure></li><li><figure><img src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/antwerp-port-epic-2021-6-1340x873.jpg\" /><figcaption>The scenery is a little different at the Antwerp Port Epic.</figcaption></figure></li><li><figure><img src=\"